Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.94,0:00:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对机动  Bloody  Murder
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快避开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,琉兹  往上跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.18,0:00:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,安可儿  我给你一次解释的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你竟敢对直人大人发起攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,即便你是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不给我一个合理的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.36,0:00:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就把你彻底破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,安可儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,琉兹  跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,快把安可儿破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,琉兹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在的运作不正常
